The 2018 MyBroadband Cloud Conference, sponsored by Liquid Telecom, has kicked off at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand. Speakers at the conference include Liquid Telecom SA CEO Reshaad Sha, Connection Telecom Marketing Director Sacha Matulovich, and Amazon Web Services’ Michael Needham. Delegates will also hear from First Distribution’s Kevin Derman, Siatik’s Brett StClair, Microsoft’s Joachim Hammer, Huawei’s Muhammed Seedat, Oracle’s Nevada Gordon, and Tarsus on Demand’s Kathryn Tindale. There will also be a panel discussion which features four cloud and hosting experts – Andrew Moodley from Axiz, Jan Hnizdo from Teraco, Darryl Govender from Synthesis, and Jon Hamlet from Symantec. You can watch the conference live via the stream below, thanks to Antfarm. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>